#

Classic Coleslaw

15 min
$5
200 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

Eggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Side Dish

Tags:

Side DishEasySummerBBQ

Description

A fresh, crunchy side dish that pairs perfectly with barbecued meats or sandwiches.

Ingredients

  • green cabbage: 4 cups, shredded
  • carrots: 1 cup, shredded
  • mayonnaise: 1/2 cup
  • apple cider vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • sugar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/4 teaspoon
